                        <interp inst="t18480403-1077-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>.</hi> Aged 24.—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy by the Jury.—
<rs id="t18480403-1077-punishment-98" type="punishmentDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18480403-1077-punishment-98" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
