                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1077-18480403 t18480403-1077-punishment-98"></join>Confined Six Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Justice Erle and the Third Jury.</hi>
               </p>
